#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:1
msgid "ACL Graph"
msgstr "ACL 计算图"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:3
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:5
msgid ""
"ACL Graph is the Ascend realization of vLLM static graph execution. "
"Upstream vLLM and PyTorch documents already describe the generic graph "
"model, including `CUDAGraphMode`, runtime dispatch, batch descriptors, "
"bucketing and padding, and the definitions of full graph and piecewise "
"graph. This document focuses on what is specific to Ascend in `vllm-"
"ascend`: the platform integration points, the extra constraints "
"introduced by ACL graph capture, and the mechanisms used to keep "
"attention parameters correct during replay."
msgstr ""
"ACL 计算图是 vLLM 静态图执行在 Ascend 平台上的实现。上游 vLLM 和 PyTorch "
"文档已经描述了通用的计算图模型，包括 `CUDAGraphMode`、运行时调度、批次描述符、分桶与填充，以及完整图和分段图的定义。本文档重点介绍 "
"`vllm-ascend` 中 Ascend 特有的内容：平台集成点、ACL 计算图捕获引入的额外约束，以及在重放期间保持注意力参数正确的机制。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:7
msgid ""
"On Ascend, the design goal is the same as upstream static graph "
"execution: reduce host launch overhead for small and medium runtime "
"shapes. The implementation boundary is different. vLLM provides the "
"generic dispatch path, while `vllm-ascend` supplies the platform wrapper,"
" capture-size trimming, and attention-specific update logic needed by ACL"
" graph replay."
msgstr ""
"在 Ascend 上，设计目标与上游静态图执行相同：减少中小型运行时形状的主机启动开销。实现边界有所不同。vLLM 提供通用的调度路径，而 "
"`vllm-ascend` 则提供平台封装器、捕获大小裁剪以及 ACL 计算图重放所需的注意力特定更新逻辑。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:9
msgid "Prerequisites and References"
msgstr "先决条件与参考资料"

