"[Accelerating PyTorch with CUDA Graphs](https://pytorch.org/blog"
"/accelerating-pytorch-with-cuda-graphs/)."
msgstr ""
"PyTorch 关于通用捕获和重放语义的计算图文档：[使用 CUDA 计算图加速 "
"PyTorch](https://pytorch.org/blog/accelerating-pytorch-with-cuda-graphs/)。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:13
msgid ""
"Ascend user guide for operational enablement: [Graph Mode "
"Guide](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.html)."
msgstr ""
"Ascend 用户指南中的操作启用说明：[计算图模式指南](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/user_guide/feature_guide/graph_mode.html)。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/Design_Documents/ACL_Graph.md:14
