#~ msgid "Why do we need ACL Graph?"
#~ msgstr "为什么需要 ACL 计算图？"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In LLM inference, each token requires"
#~ " nearly a thousand operator executions. "
#~ "When host launching operators are slower"
#~ " than device, it will cause host "
#~ "bound. In severe cases, the device "
#~ "will be idle for more than half"
#~ " of the time. To solve this "
#~ "problem, we use graph in LLM "
#~ "inference."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "在 LLM 推理中，每个 Token "
#~ "需要近千个算子的执行。当主机侧下发算子的速度慢于设备侧执行速度时，会导致主机侧瓶颈。严重情况下，设备侧空闲时间超过一半。为了解决这个问题，我们在"
#~ " LLM 推理中使用计算图。"

#~ msgid "How to use ACL Graph?"
#~ msgstr "如何使用 ACL 计算图？"

#~ msgid "How it works?"
#~ msgstr "工作原理是什么？"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "In short, graph mode works in two"
#~ " steps: **capture and replay**. When "
#~ "the engine starts, we capture all "
#~ "of the ops in the model forward"
#~ " and save it as a graph. When"
#~ " a request comes in, we just "
#~ "replay the graph on the device and"
#~ " wait for the result."
#~ msgstr "简而言之，计算图模式分为两步：**捕获与回放**。引擎启动时，我们捕获模型前向中的所有算子并保存为计算图。当请求到达时，我们只需在设备上回放该计算图并等待结果。"

#~ msgid "But in reality, graph mode is not that simple."
#~ msgstr "但实际上，计算图模式并没有那么简单。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Due to the fact that a graph "
#~ "can only replay the ops captured "
#~ "before, without doing tiling and "
#~ "checking graph input, we need to "
#~ "ensure the consistency of the graph "
#~ "input. However, we know that the "
#~ "model input's shape depends on the "
#~ "request scheduled by the Scheduler, so"
#~ " we can't ensure consistency."
#~ msgstr "由于计算图只能回放之前捕获的算子，且无法进行分块计算和检查图输入，我们需要保证计算图输入的一致性。然而，模型输入的形状取决于调度器调度的请求，因此我们无法保证输入的一致性。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Obviously, we can solve this problem "
#~ "by capturing the biggest shape and "
#~ "padding all of the model inputs to"
#~ " it. But this will bring a lot"
#~ " of redundant computing and make "
#~ "performance worse. So we can capture "
#~ "multiple graphs with different shapes, "
#~ "and pad the model input to the "
#~ "nearest graph, which will greatly reduce"
#~ " redundant computing. But when "
#~ "`max_num_batched_tokens` is very large, the"
#~ " number of graphs that need to "
#~ "be captured will also become very "
#~ "large. We know that when the input"
#~ " tensor's shape is large, the "
#~ "computing time will be very long, "
#~ "and graph mode is not necessary in"
#~ " this case. So all of the "
#~ "things we need to do are:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "显然，我们可以通过捕获最大形状并将所有模型输入填充到该形状来解决此问题。但这会带来大量冗余计算，导致性能下降。因此，我们可以捕获多个不同形状的计算图，并将模型输入填充到最接近的计算图形状，这可以大幅减少冗余计算。但当"
#~ " `max_num_batched_tokens` "
#~ "非常大时，需要捕获的计算图数量也会变得非常大。我们知道，当输入张量形状较大时，计算时间会很长，这种情况下计算图模式并非必要。因此，我们需要做的是："

#~ msgid "Set a threshold;"
#~ msgstr "设置一个阈值；"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When `num_scheduled_tokens` is bigger than "
#~ "the threshold, use `eager_mode`;"
#~ msgstr "当 `num_scheduled_tokens` 大于阈值时，使用 `eager_mode`；"

#~ msgid "Capture multiple graphs within a range below the threshold;"
#~ msgstr "在阈值以下的范围内捕获多个计算图；"

#~ msgid "Piecewise and Full graph"
#~ msgstr "分段计算图与完整计算图"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Due to the increasing complexity of "
#~ "the attention layer in current LLMs, "
#~ "we can't ensure all types of "
#~ "attention can run in graph. In "
#~ "MLA, prefill_tokens and decode_tokens have "
#~ "different calculation methods, so when a"
#~ " batch has both prefills and decodes"
#~ " in MLA, graph mode is difficult "
#~ "to handle this situation."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "由于当前 LLM 中注意力层的复杂性日益增加，我们无法保证所有类型的注意力都能在计算图中运行。在 MLA"
#~ " 中，prefill_tokens 和 decode_tokens "
#~ "有不同的计算方法，因此当批次中同时包含预填充和解码时，计算图模式难以处理这种情况。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "vLLM solves this problem with piecewise"
#~ " graph mode. We use eager mode "
#~ "to launch attention's ops, and use "
#~ "graph to deal with others. But "
#~ "this also brings some problems: The "
#~ "cost of launching ops has become "
#~ "large again. Although much smaller than"
#~ " eager mode, it will also lead "
#~ "to host bound when the CPU is "
#~ "poor or `num_tokens` is small."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "vLLM 通过分段计算图模式解决了这个问题。我们使用 eager "
#~ "模式下发注意力算子，而使用计算图处理其他算子。但这也会带来一些问题：算子下发的开销再次变大。虽然相比 eager "
#~ "模式小很多，但当 CPU 性能较差或 `num_tokens` 较小时，仍会导致主机侧瓶颈。"

#~ msgid "Altogether, we need to support both piecewise and full graph mode."
#~ msgstr "总之，我们需要同时支持分段计算图模式和完整计算图模式。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When attention can run in graph, "
#~ "we tend to choose full graph mode"
#~ " to achieve optimal performance;"
#~ msgstr "当注意力可以在计算图中运行时，我们倾向于选择完整计算图模式以获得最优性能；"

#~ msgid "When full graph does not work, use piecewise graph as a substitute;"
#~ msgstr "当完整计算图不适用时，使用分段计算图作为替代；"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When piecewise graph's performance is "
#~ "not good and full graph mode is"
#~ " blocked, separate prefills and decodes,"
#~ " and use full graph mode in "
#~ "**decode_only** situations. Because when a "
#~ "batch includes prefill requests, usually "
#~ "`num_tokens` will be quite big and "
#~ "not cause host bound."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "当分段计算图性能不佳且完整计算图模式被阻塞时，将预填充和解码分开，在 **decode_only** "
#~ "情况下使用完整计算图模式。因为当批次中包含预填充请求时，通常 `num_tokens` 会较大，不会导致主机侧瓶颈。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Currently, due to stream resource "
#~ "constraint, we can only support a "
#~ "few buckets in piecewise graph mode "
#~ "now, which will cause redundant "
#~ "computing and may lead to performance"
#~ " degradation compared with eager mode."
#~ msgstr "目前，由于流资源限制，分段计算图模式仅支持少量桶，这会导致冗余计算，与 eager 模式相比可能带来性能下降。"

#~ msgid "How is it implemented?"
#~ msgstr "实现方式是什么？"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When in graph mode, vLLM will call"
#~ " `current_platform.get_static_graph_wrapper_cls` to get"
#~ " the current device's graph model "
#~ "wrapper, so what we need to do "
#~ "is implement the graph mode wrapper "
#~ "on Ascend: `ACLGraphWrapper`."
msgstr ""
"在计算图模式下，vLLM 会调用 "
"`current_platform.get_static_graph_wrapper_cls` "
"获取当前设备的计算图模型包装器，因此我们需要在 Ascend "
"上实现计算图模式包装器：`ACLGraphWrapper`。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "vLLM has added `support_torch_compile` "
#~ "decorator to all models. This decorator"
#~ " will replace the `__init__` and "
#~ "`forward` interface of the model class."
#~ " When `forward` is called, the code"
#~ " inside the `ACLGraphWrapper` will be "
#~ "executed, and it will do capture "
#~ "or replay as mentioned above."
msgstr ""
"vLLM 已为所有模型添加了 `support_torch_compile` "
"装饰器。该装饰器会替换模型类的 `__init__` 和 `forward` 接口。当调用"
" `forward` 时，将执行 `ACLGraphWrapper` "
"内的代码，并根据上述说明进行捕获或回放。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When using piecewise graph, we just "
#~ "need to follow the above-mentioned "
#~ "process. But when in full graph, "
#~ "due to the complexity of the "
#~ "attention, sometimes we need to update"
#~ " attention op's params before execution."
#~ " So we implement `update_attn_params` and"
#~ " `update_mla_attn_params` functions for full "
#~ "graph mode. During forward, memory will"
#~ " be reused between different ops, so"
#~ " we can't update attention op's "
#~ "params before forward. In ACL Graph, "
#~ "we use `torch.npu.graph_task_update_begin` and "
#~ "`torch.npu.graph_task_update_end` to do it, "
#~ "and use `torch.npu.ExternalEvent` to ensure"
#~ " order between param updates and op"
#~ " executions."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "使用分段计算图时，只需遵循上述流程。但在完整计算图模式下，由于注意力机制的复杂性，有时需要在执行前更新注意力算子的参数。因此，我们为完整计算图模式实现了"
#~ " `update_attn_params` 和 `update_mla_attn_params` "
#~ "函数。在前向传播过程中，不同算子之间会复用内存，因此无法在前向传播之前更新注意力算子的参数。在 ACL 计算图中，我们使用"
#~ " `torch.npu.graph_task_update_begin` 和 "
#~ "`torch.npu.graph_task_update_end` 来实现此功能，并使用 "
#~ "`torch.npu.ExternalEvent` 来确保参数更新与算子执行之间的顺序。"

#~ msgid "DFX"
#~ msgstr "DFX"

#~ msgid "Stream resource constraint"
#~ msgstr "流资源限制"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Currently, we can only capture 1800 "
#~ "graphs at most, due to the "
#~ "limitation of ACL graph that a "
#~ "graph requires at least a separate "
#~ "stream. This number is bounded by "
#~ "the number of streams, which is "
#~ "2048; we save 248 streams as a "
#~ "buffer. Besides, there are many "
#~ "variables that can affect the number "
#~ "of buckets:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "目前，由于 ACL 计算图要求每个图至少需要一个独立的流，我们最多只能捕获 1800 "
#~ "个计算图。此数量受限于流的总数（2048 个），我们保留了 248 "
#~ "个流作为缓冲区。此外，还有许多变量会影响桶的数量："

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Piecewise graph divides the model into"
#~ " `num_hidden_layers + 1` sub modules, "
#~ "based on the attention layer. Every "
#~ "sub module is a single graph which"
#~ " needs to cost a stream, so the"
#~ " number of buckets in piecewise graph"
#~ " mode is very tight compared with "
#~ "full graph mode."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "分段计算图根据注意力层将模型划分为 `num_hidden_layers + 1` "
#~ "个子模块。每个子模块是一个独立的计算图，需要消耗一个流，因此与完整计算图模式相比，分段计算图模式下的桶数量非常紧张。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The number of streams required for "
#~ "a graph is related to the number"
#~ " of comm domains. Each comm domain"
#~ " will increase one stream consumed by"
#~ " a graph."
#~ msgstr "计算图所需的流数量与通信域的数量相关。每个通信域会增加计算图消耗的一个流。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When multi-stream is explicitly called"
#~ " in a sub module, it will "
#~ "consume an additional stream."
#~ msgstr "当在子模块中显式调用多流时，会额外消耗一个流。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "There are some other rules about "
#~ "ACL Graph and stream. Currently, we "
#~ "use func `update_aclgraph_sizes` to calculate"
#~ " the maximum number of buckets and"
#~ " update `graph_batch_sizes` to ensure "
#~ "stream resource is sufficient."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "关于 ACL 计算图和流还有一些其他规则。目前，我们使用 `update_aclgraph_sizes`"
#~ " 函数来计算最大桶数量并更新 `graph_batch_sizes`，以确保流资源充足。"

#~ msgid "We will expand the stream resource limitation in the future."
#~ msgstr "未来我们将放宽流资源的限制。"

#~ msgid "Limitations"
#~ msgstr "限制"

#~ msgid "`FULL` and `FULL_AND_PIECEWISE` are not supported now;"
#~ msgstr "目前不支持 `FULL` 和 `FULL_AND_PIECEWISE`；"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "When use ACL Graph and MTP and "
#~ "`num_speculative_tokens > 1`, as vLLM "
#~ "don't support this case in v0.11.0, "
#~ "we need to set `cudagraph_capture_sizes` "
#~ "explicitly."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "当使用 ACL 计算图和 MTP 且 "
#~ "`num_speculative_tokens > 1` 时，由于 vLLM 在"
#~ " v0.11.0 版本中不支持此场景，需要显式设置 `cudagraph_capture_sizes`。"

#~ msgid "`use_inductor` is not supported now;"
#~ msgstr "目前不支持 `use_inductor`；"
